			  	Slowly being discovered as well that devices that were generally percieved as useless or near useless arn't. Some will gain potential value next set too.<br />
<br />
Well, Sylex, sure, designs end up largely being the same generally. But Archspace is more about battles than designs. Designs are merely a component of AS combat that allow you to customize your ships and give them names. Customization that potentially can change battles quite significantly as well. There is NO ultimate design. Such a thing does not exist. Circumstances of battle determine what good designs are. With races becoming more and more individualized, this is even more true. AS is vastely more complex than most people think.			   <P align=right></P>
